- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used correctly for 3 patterns on .NET 7+ (L13-24)
- ✅ `#if NET7_0_OR_GREATER` with `Compiled` fallback for those 3 patterns
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ `.All()` (L159)
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `ToLowerInvariant()` correctly (L189)
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` uses `char.IsAsciiLetterOrDigit` — optimal (L254)
